body_html: It seems that you compiled clang from source, but it's not supported by NVIDIA either (it's clang vs Apple clang 😉). You need to go to the Apple Developer site and download "Command Line Tools for XCode vX.Y.Z" where X.Y.Z is either 7.3.1 or 8.0.0
